partnerDetails.about:
Integrata is an experienced electrical contracting company located on the Northern Beaches in Sydney. We work in the buildings and commercial facility space and specialize in Building Automation and Mechanical Electrical services. 

We have been established since 2003 we have a strong track record in achieving outstanding results for our customers and their properties. Integrata collaboratively works with a wide variety of customers including Macquarie University, UNSW, Equans, Airmaster, Schneider Electric, Johnson Controls, Controlworks, Frasers Property, and many others.

 

Our ethos of delivering remarkable service is embedded throughout our company culture and drives every action we take.

Products and Services

 

  • Building Automation System installation commissioning and integration.
  • Mechanical Electrical design and installation for HVAC systems.
  • MSSB and Control panel building
  • Energy Metering, sub-metering and reporting on Electrical, Water, Gas.
  • NABERS Electrical meter validations
  • EV Charging Stations
  • Communications and structured cabling Fiber and ethernet.
  • Home Automation Systems(CBUS and DYNALITE)
  • IoT (Internet of things)
  • Remote monitoring of conditions. Temperature,
  • Humidity, Light, Mould, Vibration, Sound over wifi or 4G signal.
